{
  "stem": "14142.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 423.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It started to-- it wasn't the same, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What changed, they used to say that in the government, in the Polish government, German people came in, like, like spies, you know?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even the Polish government didn't know it of them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So and they started to rule already against Jews, not to buy in the stores, not to-- how to say-- slaughter them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a shochet, for instance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They, they said that they shouldn't work, shouldn't kill the chicken the way Jews supposed to, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we felt already that it's, it's not the same.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Even in school, you know, it's-- they looked at us differently [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] till '39, 1939.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I noticed mostly the-- when, when they came, when, when the war started in Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then, we noticed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the business.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother was suffering because, for instance, we had to pay-- what's it-- like income tax, like business tax.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had a business.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then they looked, for instance, on the cleanness, and the restaurant should be perfectly, perfectly clean.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Even it was perfect clean, they was-- they were trying to find something, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Said it's not correct.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's this and this, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was trouble.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we tried.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We tried to-- especially my sister was that time helping in the restaurant.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We tried in the evening to wash everything, to make clean, you know, because we knew that maybe they will come in, the inspector, health inspector, like.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he ca-- when he'll come in, he shouldn't find something wrong.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So and he paid special attention more on us because it was in the same street another restaurant.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't pay as much attention there as they paid on us, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mother-- because we're Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
